Entry.JapaneseText: 交代の時間よ。……えっ、まだ遊び足りない？ じゃあ、また並びなさい。……えっ、並ぶのいや？
Entry.EnglishText: It's time, huh? You haven't played enough for your liking? Then get back in line. What, you hate standing in line?

Entry.JapaneseText: あなたには失望したわ！
……なんて、ウソよ。 遊んでくれて、ありがとう……またね。
Entry.EnglishText: ...Well, that's a lie. Thank you for playing... See you again.
